REQUIREMENTS: 

Introduction:
the game called “snake” or “snake game” typically involve the player controlling a line or snake, there is no official version for game, so gameplay varies. the most common version of game involves the snake or line eating items or food which make it longer.

Features of snake game:
Player can start a new game and choose the difficulty level.
he can adjust the speed of the snake movement.
He can view his score card.
Benefits:
Can learn about spatial awareness
Can plan ahead to our next moves

